	<summary>
	3/24/1994--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow the deduction as capital expenditures of preproductive or removal costs and 80 percent of special replanting costs for replanting plants destroyed by freezing temperatures, disease, drought, pests, or casualty.

